<p>Google built GBP into an active engagement surface. For retailers, that means real-time product inventory through Merchant Center. For service businesses, it means appointment booking, Q&amp;A, and post activity. For restaurants, it means menus, wait times, and reservation links.</p>
<p>The platform expects ongoing input. It rewards the businesses that provide it.</p>
